  "description": "In <i>Slime Nemesis</i> the player helps Rusty Jim to complete his practical test to become a slime exterminator. To succeed with the test Jim must defend the school wall from 20 waves of slime. Every wave is guarded by creatures that bounces around the screen. Shooting at these creatures will make them stop moving for some time. After each level there is a bonus round where coins falls from the sky. During the bonus round the player can not use the flame thrower to shoot at the guarding creatures. After the bonus round the player can use the collected coins in &quot;Slimekiller Inc. General store&quot; to buy upgrades. ",
